			<h4><a id="comment_link_64531819" name="comment_link_64531819" href="//slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23349589&amp;cid=64531819" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(64531819)" >They're not addressing the real problem</a>


		 	<span id="comment_score_64531819" class="score"> (<a href="#" onclick="getModalPrefs('modcommentlog', 'Moderation Comment Log', 64531819); return false"><span class=opt>Score:</span>3</a>)</span></h4>
		</div>
		<div class="details">
			<span class="by"><span class="byby">by </span><a href="//slashdot.org/~Baron_Yam">Baron_Yam</a>  <span class="uid"><a href="//slashdot.org/~Baron_Yam">( 643147 )</a></span></a></span><span class="writes" style="display:none"> writes:</span> 
